    </div>

    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-4 order-md-2 mb-4">
        <h4 class="d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center mb-3">
          <span class="text-muted">결제 체크아웃</span>
          <!-- 전체 상품 -->
          <span class="badge badge-secondary badge-pill">0 개</span>
        </h4>

        <div class="card mb-3">
          <div class="card-header">배송지 <span class="btn btn-sm btn-link">(주소 선택)</span></div>
          <div class="card-body">
            <div class="mb-2"><i class="fas fa-address-card mr-1"></i> 홍길동</div>
            <div class="mb-2">서울특별시 구로구 고척동 95-130 (203호)</div>
            <div>연락처: +821042090323</div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <ul class="list-group mb-3">
          <li class="list-group-item d-flex justify-content-between lh-condensed">
            <h6 class="my-0">주문 금액</h6>
            <span class="text-muted">00,000 원</span>
          </li>
          <li class="list-group-item d-flex justify-content-between lh-condensed">
            <h6 class="my-0">할인 금액</h6>
            <span class="text-muted">00,000 원</span>
          </li>
          <li class="list-group-item d-flex justify-content-between lh-condensed">
            <h6 class="my-0">배송비</h6>
            <span class="text-muted">00,000 원</span>
          </li>
          <li class="list-group-item d-flex justify-content-between bg-light">
            <div class="text-success">
              <h6 class="my-0">쿠폰</h6>
              <small>EXAMPLECODE</small>
            </div>
            <span class="text-success">-0,000 원</span>
          </li>
          <li class="list-group-item d-flex justify-content-between">
            <span>전체 금액 (KRW)</span>
            <strong>00,000 원</strong>
          </li>
        </ul>

        <form class="card p-2">
          <div class="input-group">
            <input type="text" class="form-control" placeholder="쿠폰 코드">
            <div class="input-group-append">
              <button type="submit" class="btn btn-secondary">적용</button>
            </div>
          </div>
        </form>
        <div class="card p-2 mt-3">
            <div class="clearfix px-2 my-2">
              <span class="float-left"><strong>자동결제</strong> <i class="far fa-question-circle ml-1"></i></span>
              <label class="switch float-right">
                <input type="checkbox">
                <span class="slider round"></span>
              </label>
            </div>
            <button class="btn btn-md btn-block btn-primary" type="submit" id="signup" name="signup">계속</button>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="col-md-8 order-md-1">
        <h4 class="mb-3">구매하는 상품</h4>

        <!-- 판매자 1 -->
        <div class="card mb-4">
          <div class="card-header">
            판매자명
